SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM (
    SELECT DISTINCT [v].[PONo], [v].[CompletedPer], [v].[CompletedQty], [v].[Customer], [v].[EntryDate], [v].[ExFactory], [v].[FactoryID], [v].[Fit], [v].[FulfillmentType], [v].[LastSyncedAt], [v].[Module], [v].[OrderID], [v].[OrderRemark], [v].[OrderStatus], [v].[POQty], [v].[ProcessCode], [v].[ProcessName], [v].[Product], [v].[SONo], [v].[Season], [v].[Source], [v].[Style]
    FROM [vw_OrderList] AS [v]
    WHERE ([v].[FactoryID] = @___UserTokenInfo_FactoryID_0) AND ([v].[OrderStatus] = 1)
) AS [t]

SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM (
    SELECT DISTINCT [v].[PONo], [v].[CompletedPer], [v].[CompletedQty], [v].[Customer], [v].[EntryDate], [v].[ExFactory], [v].[FactoryID], [v].[Fit], [v].[FulfillmentType], [v].[LastSyncedAt], [v].[Module], [v].[OrderID], [v].[OrderRemark], [v].[OrderStatus], [v].[POQty], [v].[ProcessCode], [v].[ProcessName], [v].[Product], [v].[SONo], [v].[Season], [v].[Source], [v].[Style]

) AS [t]

FROM [vw_ProcessDefinition] AS [v]
WHERE [v].[FactoryID] = @___UserTokenInfo_FactoryID_0
